Final prediction (Test) using the optimal model

julia> model = lwplsrda(nlvdis = res.nlvdis[u], metric = res.metric[u], h = res.h[u], 
           k = res.k[u], nlv = res.nlv[u])
Jchemo.JchemoModel{typeof(lwplsrda), Base.Pairs{Symbol, Any, NTuple{5, Symbol}, @NamedTuple{nlvdis::Int64, metric::Symbol, h::Float64, k::Int64, nlv::Int64}}}(Jchemo.lwplsrda, nothing, Base.Pairs{Symbol, Any, NTuple{5, Symbol}, @NamedTuple{nlvdis::Int64, metric::Symbol, h::Float64, k::Int64, nlv::Int64}}(:nlvdis => 10, :metric => :mah, :h => 1.0, :k => 200, :nlv => 10))

julia> fit!(model, Xtrain, ytrain)
